==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Midget
<hw>Midg"et</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Dim. of
<ets>midge</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A minute
bloodsucking fly.</def> <mark>[Local, U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A very diminutive person having normal proportions
of the body parts; compare <contr>dwarf</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Midgut</ent>⟦br⟧
